<title type="html"><![CDATA[3/5 (Thu.) Questions &amp; Answers on COVID-19 from European and USA CDC / 5 Ways To Boost Your Immune System (Host: Cammy)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=368&amp;p=385#p385"><![CDATA[
<span style="color: #FF0000">*** Removal Notice ***<br />Thursday gathering of Royal English Club is relocated to Ikari Coffee 怡客咖啡, 台北市中正區衡陽路116號.</span><br /><br /><br />Session I: Questions &amp; Answers on COVID-19 from European and USA CDC<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.ecdc.europa.eu/en/novel-coronavirus-china/questions-answers">https://www.ecdc.europa.eu/en/novel-cor ... ns-answers</a><!-- m --><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/downloads/2019-ncov-factsheet.pdf">https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-nc ... tsheet.pdf</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Q1: What are the symptoms of COVID-19 infection? What is the mode of transmission? How does it spread? Please share your knowledge with your table members.<br />Q2: How can I avoid getting infected from COVID-19? Please share your thoughts and tips. <br />Q3: What should I be most cautious of when travelling abroad, including trips to China? What personal items will you prepare to bring to China? <br />Q4: What touching story did you have heard since the outbreak of Wuhan pneumonia (COVID-19) Please share with your table members<br /><br />Extended reading <br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://chinapost.nownews.com/20200217-996594">https://chinapost.nownews.com/20200217-996594</a><!-- m --><br />Q5: What can you do when eyeglasses fogging up while wearing a face mask? Please share your experimental experience from this news. <br /><br /><br />-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br /><br /><br />Session II: 5 WAYS TO BOOST YOUR IMMUNE SYSTEM<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.fitnessfirst.com.sg/blog/5-ways-to-boost-your-immune-system">https://www.fitnessfirst.com.sg/blog/5- ... une-system</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Q1: With no vaccine for Covid-19 currently, we do to boost our immune system for fighting against the virus. Why do you agree or not?<br />Q2: Regular exercise will contribute to a healthy immune system. How do you <br />schedule your exercise plan? Please share your outcome and tips. <br />Q3: How much water intake is the best for me during daily? How to executive it?  <br />Please check your answer as follows,<br />1.You rarely feel thirsty<br />2.Your urine is colorless or light yellow<br />Welcome any comments or tips at your table.<br />Q4: Please share at least two points you will try to practice in this article with your <br />table members.<br /><br /><br />==================================================================================<br /><br /><br />Agenda<br />7:00 pm-7:30 pm Free talk<br />7:30 pm-8:10 pm Session 1 discussion<br />8:10 pm-8:40 pm Presentation (At least two members of each table are invited)<br />8:40 pm-8:45 pm Break time &amp; Group picture<br />8:45 pm-9:15 pm Session 2 discussion<br />9:15 pm-9:30 pm Presentation<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=25437">Michael</a> — Fri Feb 28, 2020 9:41 am</p><hr />
